short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Antheus Nuvo Click to Dial Extension.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
This is a supporting product for the Antheus Telecom Nuvo phone system.
This extension will give users the ability to click to dial any UK number they see in web pages.

Future development will expand to include international destinations as well as more integrated features with the Nuvo system itself.

For support contact support at antheus.co.uk
